  Purpose:
  Container schema for all CAP schemas. Defines the <synopsis> element, 
  which is the root element for all other schemas; includes standard 
  attribute set for this element. Has no other CAP structured content. 
  Allows any mixed content with any foreign elements. 
  Does not allow any other CAP elements. 
  
  This schema is in intent "abstract"; we do not anticipate it would ever
  be instantiated. It can be thought of as the schema for a report of an
  unspecified procedure at an unspecified site.
  
  Dependencies:      
  direct <externalRef> to anyForeignContent.rng; must be in same folder
  direct <externalRef> to anyForeignAttributes.rng; must be in same folder
